rating_comment: Good property

The place is nice and cosy. Rooms are very spacious. Maria ma'am is an amazing host. The locality is peaceful and at a walking distance to the market. Overall experience was very good. Would definitely recommend.

My recent stay at this Airbnb property was absolutely delightful!
One of the standout features of this Airbnb is the convenient access to tuk-tuk transportation.
Furthermore, the owner was incredibly accommodating and provided excellent recommendations for local markets and must-see sights.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  路 April 2024,  路 Stayed with kids
rating_comment: Location was ok, Maria was very accommodating and friendly, rooms were pretty big and nice, the floors need to be cleaned better. Over all good experience.
It was a very rough day for Maria when we got to her place, but she took care of us right away. There is nothing more you can ask of a host. Will definitely stay there if I revisit.
Just Wow

It was very nice staying at marias place at Siliguri. The place is very good to stay for 6-7 people together. All necessary items are there. Maria also is very welcoming, polite and responsive. Marias home-cooked meals were delicious. It was an added advantage. There was an equipped kitchen also. Also she helped us with car service. I recommend her place to everyone who wants to visit siliguri for any purpose.

a very pleasant stay indeed. Maria was very helpful all along making the entire period of stay hassle free. In terms of location, it was easily accessible with pretty much all places at stones throw distance. Overall, a lovely experice staying at Marias. Thank you.

Delighted with the homestay experience! The host was incredibly accommodating and addressed all my concerns.
My parents and relatives thoroughly enjoyed their stay. The host's assistance and hospitality made the trip worry-free. Highly recommended!
Fantastic stay
Great Host, always responsive and a warm place to stay

The best place to stay and feel like home. Rooms and kitchen were just amazing. Every necessary thing was there and specially the host Maria was so amazing, always responsive, fed us good food. It was a nice experience in Marias Home stay.

We had a excellent experience at Marias homestay. Maria is extremely welcoming, helpful and we immediately felt at home when we reached after a tiring road journey from Kolkata. The rooms are very clean and entire house is aesthetically decorated and cozy. The kitchen is fully functional however Maria and her daughter served us delicious home cooked dinner which was a plus. We loved the stay and would love to visit again!!
Maria and her family are lovely. The place is nice, comfy and it has everything you need - we felt welcome and would love to come again when in town

info: Rating, 5 stars,  路 December 2023,  路 Stayed with kids
rating_comment: Maria made us feel at home from the moment we arrived at her place. She was very flexible with our requests as we had large group of seven including a two year old toddler. Although we only stayed for one night we thoroughly enjoyed our stay. We all left the place quite satisfied and would recommend her place to future guests
Comfortable stay, spacious for a family for 4. Friendly hosts, and great home cooked food
Our stay for 2 nights was wonderful. The house was to ourselves and it matched the description. Hosts were proactive and overall a convenient stay. Thank you

We booked Marias homestay as we had to board an early morning train from NJP. We absolutely loved our time there. She cooked delicious meals for us and treated us like her own children. Even stephen uncle and maria aunty went out of their way to drop us three girls to the NJP station at 4 am in the morning. This is something you can only expect from a guardian. I will be recommending my friends and family to visit maria aunty whenever they visit Siliguri
Nice place

It was a so lovely staying at Maria's with my family including my baby and our cat. The location was easy to find. Maria aunty and family were extremely sweet to have installed a washing machine and aqua guard upon our arrival. Such thoughtful and kind hosts.
House is extremely cozy, comfortable and clean. The bedrooms were spacious and bathrooms are clean. We thank them for a wonderful stay.

prime located property..very nice host.. Specious rooms with well equipped kitchen..
recommend if u wanna enjoy ur stay in prime located property in Siliguri
Peaceful friendly
The host was very polite and the place was exactly as it was described with clean rooms and good hospitality:)
